Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.60,0:00:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.74,0:00:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.21,0:00:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.49,0:00:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.33,0:00:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.94,0:00:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.28,0:01:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.56,0:01:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.59,0:01:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.86,0:01:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正当我们\N到处追捕奈落的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.16,0:01:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却遭到\N恐怖的长毛妖怪的袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在危险之际\N幸亏钢牙突然出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.90,0:01:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才帮助我们脱离险境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.14,0:01:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到却碰到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.11,0:01:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路不停寻找钢牙的\N妖狼族女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.41,0:01:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明答应过要娶我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太勉强自己知不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.58,0:02:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不管有多辛苦都别忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.38,0:02:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还可以嫁给我  菖蒲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.99,0:02:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.26,0:02:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的这么说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.26,0:02:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的说过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.46,0:02:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第84话 速度超快的准新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.80,0:02:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说那个妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.07,0:02:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奈落特地派来的刺客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他拷问一下不就知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.61,0:02:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定\N妖怪知道奈落躲在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.05,0:02:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题\N等救戈薇出来之后再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要没事  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.16,0:02:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你这么说  菖蒲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.23,0:02:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖狼族的长老就是你爷爷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长老就是我爷爷没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.83,0:02:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你这次急急忙忙下山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近不知道为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北边山对面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.01,0:03:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是传来一阵奇怪的妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.31,0:03:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.65,0:03:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说那是魔鬼的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.49,0:03:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了抢地盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东边  北边  南边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.39,0:03:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有西边各个妖狼族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.56,0:03:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家吵得你死我活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷为了平息这些纷争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.30,0:03:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望\N我嫁一个有势力的年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把族里的力量团结起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是政治联姻吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.34,0:03:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好\N我早就已经跟钢牙有婚约了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.58,0:03:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过很多次我不记得了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.05,0:03:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷也认为钢牙一定有办法\N让族里团结起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我自己也很愿意嫁给他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.02,0:03:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说\N应该不是单纯的政治联姻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.59,0:03:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人真没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻到一点邪气\N就被吓成这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.39,0:03:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且不管我\N是不是能够整合众人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.33,0:03:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实\N只要能够制服他们不就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.33,0:03:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情并没有你想的那么简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.77,0:04:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要整合族里的人\N首先得得到大家的信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.04,0:04:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说就是个性要沉着稳重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.17,0:04:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你这么说\N这项任务更不适合我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.18,0:04:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在对我来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.05,0:04:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的\N是把奈落的脑袋砍下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.42,0:04:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于其他的问题\N等以后有空再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.35,0:04:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不答应了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回山上去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.13,0:04:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲  你都这么大了\N别老是爷爷长爷爷短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.93,0:04:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做才对\N应该自己拿定主意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话就说到这里为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.21,0:04:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等  钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.65,0:04:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.32,0:04:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉这只臭笨狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.32,0:04:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子这次又让妖怪跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.66,0:04:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.72,0:04:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看妖怪很快就会到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.16,0:05:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆回去找犬夜叉他们算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着担心  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别怕  我会保护你一辈子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很谢谢你一番好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.24,0:05:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这个时候\N不适合谈我跟你之间的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.41,0:05:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙口口声声说\N喜欢这个女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.12,0:05:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫戈薇的女孩子\N难道她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.86,0:05:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭妖怪  出来接招吧\N别老是躲起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.36,0:05:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷有话问你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.76,0:05:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.37,0:05:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长毛妖来袭击我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.77,0:05:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.87,0:05:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道妖怪想要困住我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你马上去找戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.21,0:05:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.08,0:05:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  我来救你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.09,0:06:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你跑不掉了吧  死家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.22,0:06:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟你那些四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.79,0:06:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我会一起吞下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.39,0:06:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲  我知道不应该麻烦你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.40,0:06:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是要拜托你\N帮我照顾戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  要我帮你照顾她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.80,0:06:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇\N你跟菖蒲乖乖待在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.97,0:06:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为有多厉害呢\N不过是块头大而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等着瞧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.19,0:06:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你不嫌烦一直紧追不舍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你顺便跟我说一声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落到底躲在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛一撮撮掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个死妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破魔之箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道戈薇是巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.35,0:07:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用怕  菖蒲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏蛋  死家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  你为什么不走呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.23,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙跟妖怪决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.96,0:07:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了要保护你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.80,0:07:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙不是这样的人\N你误会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙跟妖怪决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.24,0:07:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了保护我跟你两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.61,0:07:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.61,0:07:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.61,0:07:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.38,0:07:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是戈薇的同伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.26,0:07:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙  你在搞什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.76,0:07:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差点就害死戈薇了\N你知不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是怪你自己笨手笨脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.89,0:07:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才让妖怪有机会跑掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.27,0:07:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我负责保护戈薇就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先撤走吧  瘦皮狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.57,0:07:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇我自己会保护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能保护什么  不自量力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.44,0:08:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然犬夜叉已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以不用孤军奋战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.81,0:08:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道钢牙他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.59,0:08:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己小心点  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.09,0:08:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一\N被妖怪的头发缠住就惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用替我担心  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.19,0:08:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着看好戏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.19,0:08:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出动风之伤他就别想活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.06,0:08:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这只臭笨狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.10,0:08:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是\N在紧要关头故意出来搅局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.50,0:08:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮不到你动手我自己收拾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.24,0:08:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是你自己一厢情愿\N单恋戈薇吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.78,0:08:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你那些\N四魂之玉碎片一起吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去帮钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你还有谁能够帮他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.25,0:08:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看\N他就快要被妖怪给吃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.89,0:08:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙会不会被吃掉\N跟我有什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.90,0:08:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是四魂之玉碎片\N不能被你抢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛居然一撮撮的飞了出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.77,0:09:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.91,0:09:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人\N也别以为可以拦的住我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我总算\N臭妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.15,0:09:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算可以脱离奈落的控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的工作\N是借着四魂之玉的能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让自己恢复原形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.43,0:09:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.43,0:09:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平安没事就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.93,0:09:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女孩子是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫做菖蒲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.34,0:09:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是钢牙的未婚妻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙的未婚妻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.31,0:09:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一时也说不清\N等等再告诉你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了\N刚才那个到底是什么妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.31,0:09:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个妖怪刚刚告诉我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己已经摆脱奈落的控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.45,0:09:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭妖怪  到底搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落那个坏蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.59,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔下这座城跑的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然也不带我走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.69,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这家伙\N并不是奈落派来的分身呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.33,0:10:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奈落舍弃的部分吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.23,0:10:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像\N真的是被奈落遗弃的部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.10,0:10:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚还担心  让钢牙独力对付\N奈落的分身太残酷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.61,0:10:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙\N坏蛋妖怪扔下不要的垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.48,0:10:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然\N用尽吃奶的力量去对付他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲  不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要保护你的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.26,0:10:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你暂时乖乖待在这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.36,0:10:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这只臭笨狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等老子有空的时候\N再来陪你玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.73,0:10:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死瘦皮狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.64,0:10:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.74,0:10:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你是被奈落扔下\N或是自己逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.41,0:10:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之一句话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.51,0:10:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不知道\N奈落的行踪是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.25,0:10:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.25,0:11:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在那边犹豫什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.92,0:11:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙你不是有事要问妖怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你担心  我自有分寸\N不需要人家提醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.76,0:11:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭妖怪  你知道些什么\N一五一十的给我交代清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.27,0:11:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么搜都没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.27,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落早就逃到一个  任何人\N都奈何不了他的地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.68,0:11:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都奈何不了他的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.59,0:11:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过很可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.19,0:11:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方就连我都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.79,0:11:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是在半路上\N被奈落遗弃的倒霉鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.56,0:11:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来\N奈落会怎么做我也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.20,0:11:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们跟我一样是倒霉鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.80,0:11:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看那个家伙不像在撒谎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.57,0:11:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么线索都找不到\N又要白忙一场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.81,0:11:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然问不出个名堂\N那就没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.82,0:12:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  说不定这只倒霉妖怪\N还真的有一点用处呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.32,0:12:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙的臭妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.09,0:12:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.63,0:12:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.83,0:12:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖气又出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.73,0:12:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是菖蒲花的力量吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.64,0:12:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃了你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.84,0:12:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.47,0:12:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.74,0:12:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们被妖怪吞掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.48,0:12:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙  菖蒲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.61,0:12:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这只死妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看本少爷用风之伤劈死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.25,0:12:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于把四魂之玉碎片\N吞进肚子里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.51,0:13:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我也敢动  不想活啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.88,0:13:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙  你的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我刚刚突然跳起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.15,0:13:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小伤算不了什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.52,0:13:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股臭味\N你们给我牢牢的记住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼族兄弟们也都要记住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.04,0:13:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道钢牙\N想利用狼群找出奈落的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一次地毯式搜索吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种招数有个屁用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是狼群\N都可以嗅出奈落的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.55,0:13:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个坏蛋妖怪\N早就已经被我抓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙  跑哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.69,0:13:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇\N看样子我是不走不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.69,0:13:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我答应你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.93,0:13:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次见到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.33,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定亲手\N将奈落的脑袋带来送给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.57,0:14:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭钢牙  明明就是单相思嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我对他一片痴心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.44,0:14:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你不要这副面孔嘛戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.84,0:14:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了\N我答应过你一定会回来娶你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  钢牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.35,0:14:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在认识我之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.36,0:14:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就答应菖蒲\N等她长大要娶她为妻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过这样的话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.86,0:14:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本一点都不记得\N我说过那些话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回想一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个月光的晚上\N彩虹出现的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.37,0:14:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对菖蒲说过什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.24,0:14:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩虹出现的…晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.91,0:15:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等哪一天你离开山上的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.68,0:15:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候我要你做我的新娘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.52,0:15:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮的彩虹出现的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的一点都想不起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.17,0:15:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙  你看过天上的彩虹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.67,0:15:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过很多次\N我不记得有什么彩虹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N菖蒲为什么老是缠着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况\N那已经是小时候的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.69,0:16:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前的事我不想再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.82,0:16:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很清楚现在的你\N必须很努力直到抓到奈落为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.46,0:16:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇跟钢牙\N陷入一场三角纠纷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我看不是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定这个叫菖蒲的姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会把钢牙带回山上去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.71,0:16:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是钢牙一向都喜欢戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.71,0:16:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可不像有些坏蛋\N经常三心二意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.48,0:16:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干什么  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.12,0:16:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟爷爷\N一定设法让族人团结起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.12,0:16:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到你报了大仇为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.26,0:16:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过\N这并不代表我已经死心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点你要牢牢记住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.33,0:16:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是你未来的新娘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…做我的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.34,0:16:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须看得见四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.68,0:16:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇她…她就看得见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.24,0:17:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说能看见四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.25,0:17:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此\N我也会让自己看见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.29,0:17:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让自己能够看得见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点恐怕不容易吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.06,0:17:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.96,0:17:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.80,0:17:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说可以就可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你办不到你就办不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会开开心心一直等下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.21,0:17:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒请教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.38,0:17:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说一个人如果努力修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.32,0:17:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是可以像戈薇一样\N感觉得到四魂之玉碎片的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.72,0:17:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看应该没用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.29,0:17:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲为什么\N那么肯定能看得见呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说得那么肯定耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那丫头是个傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙  说得差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.57,0:17:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你就留下\N脚上的四魂之玉碎片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.57,0:17:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省省吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.84,0:17:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.11,0:18:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走啦  不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.08,0:18:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.11,0:18:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如看钢牙那边有多少人可以帮忙\N还比较有用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少在那边胡说八道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然臭味可以做为一种线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落又怎么可能\N扔掉自己的垃圾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.02,0:18:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾就代表臭味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.09,0:18:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落怎么可能会这么粗心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.06,0:18:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说  奈落这个坏蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.87,0:18:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不怕被人家给发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.84,0:18:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你  奈落会躲到哪去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.65,0:18:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想听听看你的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.39,0:18:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留给你自己慢慢想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.36,0:18:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的想不出来耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.33,0:18:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来得靠自己才行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.10,0:19:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实\N犬夜叉说的话一点也没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个妖怪说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落藏身在\N任何人都奈何不了他的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.58,0:19:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方到底在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.66,0:19:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个晚上应该就在桥的附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.21,0:19:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不想输给奈落那个坏蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.88,0:19:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是复仇\N也不是我唯一的人生目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.69,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你很快的\N可以忘掉月亮的彩虹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.36,0:20:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的忘不掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.39,0:20:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我一辈子也忘不了\N你说过永远都会保护我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.72,0:20:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有彩虹我也不会忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.90,0:20:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  气死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.90,0:20:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费了这么大力气\N总算破除了奈落的结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.24,0:20:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁晓得\N只要大家同心协力的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.28,0:20:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信总有一天\N一定可以找到奈落的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.75,0:20:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说大家是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.28,0:20:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会还在指望钢牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.92,0:20:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙那个家伙\N一直对你不死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.49,0:21:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你连得罪未婚妻都不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.49,0:21:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你舍得不理他吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.92,0:21:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么  难道你在吃醋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃醋?我干嘛要吃醋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.73,0:21:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没吃醋那就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.77,0:21:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你怎么说  我无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.93,0:21:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  是你自己先说的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.28,0:21:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就当作我们不存在\N继续说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.02,0:21:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说够了没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.95,0:21:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会说够呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.52,0:21:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家菖蒲对钢牙一心一意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.09,0:21:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是犬夜叉\N也能够像她那样该有多好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.13,0:21:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮的彩虹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.04,0:21:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上怎么可能会有彩虹嘛\N别作梦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.11,0:21:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.64,0:21:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有缘人一定可以看得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.24,0:21:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.29,0:22:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要流多少泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.03,0:22:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every Heart  才能坦白面对自己呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.84,0:22:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若对谁传达情感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.65,0:22:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every Heart  是否就能得到满足呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.09,0:22:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕着漫长漫长的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.56,0:22:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着遥远的星星祈祷着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.84,0:23:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.84,0:23:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都在寻找真正的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.38,0:23:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望自己能够变得更坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.06,0:23:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要抬头看着高高的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.90,0:23:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.64,0:23:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都在寻找生命的意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.59,0:23:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了\N自从奈落无缘无故失踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.76,0:23:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以往还算安份的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.42,0:23:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始蠢蠢欲动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.96,0:23:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托这些妖怪的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.49,0:23:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱魔铺的生意突然好起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.49,0:23:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过生意也比以前竞争多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个\N说自己懂得除妖的老婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.66,0:23:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置身各种妖气之中\N居然面不改色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.93,0:24:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是道行太高\N还是感觉太迟钝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.60,0:24:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看还是\N赶快收拾一下回家去算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.87,0:24:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回犬夜叉是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.17,0:24:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖气冲天的鬼头城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.44,0:24:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的公主哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.68,0:24:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这项任务就交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.95,0:24:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题没问题



